Name: storeServerSysUp
Description: Indicates that the Store Server is up and active.

Name: storeServerSysDown
Description: Indicates that the Store Server is shutting down.

Name: storeServerBusConnStatus
Description: Indicates the change in availability status of message complex.

Name: storeServerPeerConnStatus
Description: Indicates the change in peer connection status.

Name: storeServerTrapsResync
Description: Indicates the start and end of a trap resync operation.

Name: storeServerHeartbeat
Description: Sent periodically to indicate that Store Server is alive
